com.djrapitops.plugin.command

Class TreeCmdNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djrapitops.plugin.command.CommandNode
      • com.djrapitops.plugin.command.TreeCmdNode

  • public class TreeCmdNode
extends CommandNode
    CommandNode with sub-commands.

    Sub commands are defined with setNodeGroups(com.djrapitops.plugin.command.CommandNode[]...). Each TreeCmdNode is initialized with a HelpCommand that provides listing of sub-commands. It is recommended to use setColorScheme(ColorScheme) to apply chat colors to the help listings.

    It is possible to set a command to be executed with unknown arguments by using setDefaultCommand(String). If this is not set 'help' command will be executed when first argument is not a known sub-command.

    Author:
    Rsl1122
